namic resistance dyn V 1 R I tan \x11 \x01 \x01 \x11 \x12 5.', 'ELECTRICAL RESISTANCE “The electrical resistance of a conductor is the obstruction posed by the conductor to the flow of electric current through it”.', '1.', 'i.e., R = V/I JEE | NEET | Class 8 - 10 Download eSaral App www.esaral.com Rev.', 'Notes Class 12 Physics Chapter-2'], 'model': 'text-embedding-3-small', 'encoding_format': 'base64'}}
